  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Survive increasingly challenging waves, unlocking new weapons and buildings as you progress through time</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong><i><u>more than 70 weapons</u></i></strong> to fight your enemies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/291bb9ee38827f0f1bd576587fb615a4.poster.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/291bb9ee38827f0f1bd576587fb615a4.webm?t=1738952302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/291bb9ee38827f0f1bd576587fb615a4.mp4?t=1738952302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build 16 different defenses, such as the <strong><i><u>Archer Tower, Drone, Paratrooper Hangar</u></i></strong> and many other structures that advance through time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/28d0493726d764a171ab98076d3c7848.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>Recruit allies</i></u> to assist you in combat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/40168b5c0d7ca94f1cfe422ca228c41e.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Receive rewards and <strong><i><u>purchase permanent/in-game passive upgrades</u></i></strong> to strengthen allies, buildings and even weaken enemies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/fb533003310bc8121e9f986e54364558.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face dozens of random events. <u><i><strong>Vikings, vampires, bounty hunters</strong></i></u>... You never know what might come next </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/77c09d3d95dac949399a7c2244b5d4ed.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight <strong><i><u>12 unique bosses</u></i></strong> and other powerful enemies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/2b0fa01246492c84f052b9567507b3aa.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Each time you play you will find different weapons, upgrades, events, bosses... Learn your strengths and win this challenge!</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Survive increasingly challenging waves, unlocking new weapons and buildings as you progress through time</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong><i><u>more than 70 weapons</u></i></strong> to fight your enemies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/291bb9ee38827f0f1bd576587fb615a4.poster.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/291bb9ee38827f0f1bd576587fb615a4.webm?t=1738952302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/291bb9ee38827f0f1bd576587fb615a4.mp4?t=1738952302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build 16 different defenses, such as the <strong><i><u>Archer Tower, Drone, Paratrooper Hangar</u></i></strong> and many other structures that advance through time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/28d0493726d764a171ab98076d3c7848.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>Recruit allies</i></u> to assist you in combat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/40168b5c0d7ca94f1cfe422ca228c41e.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Receive rewards and <strong><i><u>purchase permanent/in-game passive upgrades</u></i></strong> to strengthen allies, buildings and even weaken enemies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/fb533003310bc8121e9f986e54364558.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face dozens of random events. <u><i><strong>Vikings, vampires, bounty hunters</strong></i></u>... You never know what might come next </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/77c09d3d95dac949399a7c2244b5d4ed.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight <strong><i><u>12 unique bosses</u></i></strong> and other powerful enemies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165310/extras/2b0fa01246492c84f052b9567507b3aa.avif?t=1738952302\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Each time you play you will find different weapons, upgrades, events, bosses... Learn your strengths and win this challenge!</i></strong></p>",
